cu.explanation_en: Setting the local S port C to 99999 exceeds the maximum allowed port number, causing configuration validation error.

du.explanation_en: Setting the number of uplink symbols to 100 exceeds the maximum allowed value, causing configuration validation error.
du.explanation_zh: 將上行符號數設定為 100 超過最大允許值，會導致配置驗證錯誤。
